{"id": "art-115", "label": "Art. 115", "title": "Art. 115: Măsurile educative", "slug": "art-115", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 115: M&#259;surile educative </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(1)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'>M&#259;surile educative sunt neprivative de libertate sau privative de\nlibertate.</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:18.65pt'><span style='color:black'>1.<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'>M&#259;surile educative neprivative de libertate sunt:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:18.65pt'><span style='color:black'>a)stagiul de formare\ncivic&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:18.65pt'><span style='color:black'>b)supravegherea;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:18.65pt'><span style='color:black'>c)consemnarea la sfâr&#351;it de\ns&#259;pt&#259;mân&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:18.65pt'><span style='color:black'>d)asistarea zilnic&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:18.65pt'><span style='color:black'>2.<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'>M&#259;surile educative privative de libertate sunt:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:18.65pt'><span style='color:black'>a)internarea într-un centru\neducativ;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:18.65pt'><span style='color:black'>b)internarea într-un centru de\ndeten&#355;ie.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(2)Alegerea m&#259;surii educative\ncare urmeaz&#259; s&#259; fie luat&#259; fa&#355;&#259; de minor se face, în\ncondi&#355;iile art. 114, potrivit criteriilor prev&#259;zute în art. 74.</span></p>"}